        This project hopes to create a conversation front-end framework for Linux and adapt to various chat platforms by implementing the Adapter back-end interface. Currently already has a backend based on oicq and Icalingua's own protocol. 
    </p>
    <p xml:lang="zh_CN">
        一款linux平台的QQ客户端
        本项目希望为 Linux 打造一个会话前端框架，通过实现 Adapter 后端接口来适配各种聊天平台。目前已经拥有基于 oicq 以及 Icalingua 自有协议的后端
    </p>
